{"tid":706463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醉洋漢圖搶槍　傷5警","createTime":"2018-06-18T02:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T03:06:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2bf7d17ead7fc69b28bd8fbf78418889a10469","tid":706463,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20423689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20423689&d=jdNRKCjb3sKG7K77ecYh1BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=08a1884e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180618%2F20423689&h=02eea32b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180618/20423689</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月18日 <br />\n<br />\n醉洋漢圖搶槍　傷5警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180618/large/16227259.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180618%2Flarge%2F16227259.jpg&h=c3ecb134&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■南丫島前日發生企圖搶槍案。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】南丫島發生企圖搶槍案。一名外籍男子疑醉酒鬧事，手持利刀與妻子發生爭執，驚動警方接報到場調查，糾纏期間，有人意圖強搶警員的佩槍，最終被5名警員合力制服。外籍男子涉案被拘捕，案件列作襲警、藏有攻擊性武器及意圖搶劫而襲擊，交由水警總區重案組跟進。事件中，有5名警員受傷送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與妻爭執　揮15吋利刀<br />\n<br />\n事發於前日下午5時許，南丫島榕樹灣後街一幢大廈天台一名49歲外籍男子疑飲酒後，與43歲姓張妻子發生爭執，有人見狀報警。<br />\n警方接報到場之後，發現該名外籍男子手持一柄長約15吋的利刀揮舞，警員見他情緒激動，於是上前嘗試制服，外籍漢反抗，混亂間涉嫌企圖搶奪其中一名警員的佩槍，但他最終被5名警員合力制服。<br />\n<br />\n糾纏期間，外籍漢耳朵受傷，5名警員分別手、面、胸受傷，各人事後同被送往瑪麗醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n涉案被捕外籍男子經治理後被轉送東區醫院留醫，警方將案件列作襲警、藏有攻擊性武器及意圖搶劫而襲擊，案件交由水警總區重案組跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n11歲童軍尼龍繩纏頸命危<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n《爆相爆片》六月第一輪揭曉"},{"pid":"0c27bcfb882b3d9897ff3bad33cc10906e30ef58","tid":706463,"uid":126779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"嘩，15吋長刀喎，警察做咩唔拔槍開槍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a677bf9df17cb442f9b0c68c60146c5d9240397","tid":706463,"uid":83097,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0c27bcfb882b3d9897ff3bad33cc10906e30ef58","tid":706463,"uid":126779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:22:18.000Z","msg":"嘩，15吋長刀喎，警察做咩唔拔槍開槍呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : Are you a HK Student?! <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : The fuck?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :  I repeat, are you studying?!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : I ain't no student.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Then everything's good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Put your guns and batons away boys. Sir you mind coming with us to the station?"},{"pid":"a8664c4c9e934b76cf516af88a60345409209291","tid":706463,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"685f305275f8aa88b9fdd9abad420c7441c329e1","tid":706463,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99af713c7c0d5822db20519b40ccb58386523381","tid":706463,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T03:06:46.000Z","msg":"香港警察冇槍嘅話,戰鬥力應該仲廢過一般人"}]}